Ing '''sistema nerviosa''' o nervous system ning animal ing manibala king 
pamangimut da reng [[:en:muscle|kalamnan]], manantabe (monitors) kareng 
[[:en:organ (anatomy)|organ]], gagawa at mag-process kareng input ibat kareng 
[[:en:sense|panamdam]] (senses), at papalyari kareng [[action 
(philosophy)|kimut]] (actions) (lon ya ing [[Central Nervous System]]). 

Kareng animal a alang [[:en:brain|utak]], e gagawa o maging daralanan da reng 
isip at kapanamdaman (emotions). Uli na niti, ya ing babye diwa o “anima” 
kareng animal (maliban kareng [[sponge]]). 

== Ing sistema nerviosa da reng vertebrate ==
Keraklan, mapipitna ya ing sistema nerviosa da reng 
[[:en:vertebrate|vertebrate]] king [[:en:central nervous system|central nervous 
system]] (CNS) ampong [[:en:peripheral nervous system|peripheral nervous 
system]] (PNS). Ing CNS bibilugan ne ning [[:en:brain|utak]] ampo ning 
[[:en:spinal cord|medula espinal]]. Ita namang PNS, bibilugan de reng 
eganaganang nervios at neuron a e kayabe king CNS. Deng keraklan kareng awsan 
dang “nerves” o nervios, (a ing katutwan axon la) tuturing do kayabe king PNS. 
Ita namang peripheral nervous system, mapipitna ya king [[:en:somatic nervous system]] 
ampo ing [[:en:autonomic nervous system]]. 

